ings geheiratet. Sie hatten mindestens 1 Sohn. Er hat sich 1513 zum Militärdienst angemeldet. 1568 ist sein Beruf als high sheriff of co. hertford in Hertford, Hertfordshire, England, United Kingdom aufgeführt. Er starb am 7. August 1517 im Alter von 27 Jahren in Richmond, Surrey, England und wurde in Caernarfonshire, Wales begraben."},"ht":{"1490–7 August 1517":"1490–7 August 1517","1490–1517":"1490–1517","1492–1553":"1492–1553","1512–1585":"1512–1585","1471–1514":"1471–1514","1474–1501":"1474–1501","1471":"1471","1492":"1492","1490":"1490","4 June 1514":"4 June 1514","4 May 1510":"4 May 1510","1514":"1514","1513":"1513","1501":"1501","1512":"1512","1553":"1553","7 August 1517":"7 August 1517","1585":"1585","1474":"1474","1517":"1517","Caernarfon, Gwynedd, Wales":"Richmond, Surrey, England","Poynings, Sussex, England":"Poynings, Sussex, Angletè, United Kingdom","Hurstmonceaux, Sussex, England":"Herstmonceux, Sussex, Angletè, United Kingdom","Scrivelsby Court, Lincolnshire, England":"Scrivelsby Court, Lincolnshire, England","Gwynedd, Wales":"Gwynedd, Pays de Galles, United Kingdom","Tredegar, Monmouthshire, Wales":"Tredegar, Monmouthshire, Wales","Caernarfonshire, Wales":"Caernarfonshire, Wales"},"hu":{"1490–7 August 1517":"1490–1517. augusztus 7.","1490–1517":"1490–1517","1492–1553":"1492–1553","1512–1585":"1512–1585","1471–1514":"1471–1514","1474–1501":"1474–1501","1471":"1471","1492":"1492","1490":"1490","4 June 1514":"1514. június 4.","4 May 1510":"1510. május 4.","1514":"1514","1513":"1513","1501":"1501","1512":"1512","1553":"1553","7 August 1517":"1517. augusztus 7.","1585":"1585","1474":"1474","1517":"1517","Caernarfon, Gwynedd, Wales":"Richmond, Surrey, England","Poynings, Sussex, England":"Poynings, Sussex, Anglia, United Kingdom","Hurstmonceaux, Sussex, England":"Herstmonceux, Sussex, Anglia, United Kingdom","Scrivelsby Court, Lincolnshire, England":"Scrivelsby Court, Lincolnshire, England","Gwynedd, Wales":"Gwynedd, Wales, United Kingdom","Tredegar, Monmo